<mvc:View controllerName="gourmeo.resources.main.controllers.App" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
    xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form"
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">
    <App id="gourmeoApp">
        <pages>
            <Page title="{i18n>loginPageTitle}" id="pageLogin">
                <content>
                    <FlexBox alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center">
                        <items>
                            <VBox class="vbox-login">
                                <items>
                                    <FlexBox alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center" class="sapUiMediumMargin">
                                        <items>
                                            <Image src="imgs/brand/gourmeo_logo_web.png" width="200px" height="200px" />
                                        </items>
                                    </FlexBox>
                                    <Label labelFor="txtUserId" text="{i18n>loginUserLabel}" />
                                    <Input id="txtUserId" placeholder="{i18n>userInputPlaceholder}" submit="onLoginBtnPress"/>
                                    <Label labelFor="txtPassword" text="{i18n>loginUserPassword}" />
                                    <Input id="txtPassword" placeholder="{i18n>passwordInputPlaceholder}" type="Password" submit="onLoginBtnPress"/>
                                    <Button text="{i18n>btnLogin}" type="Emphasized" press="onLoginBtnPress" width="100%" class="sapUiSmallMarginTop"/>
                                    <HBox alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center" class="sapUiSmallMarginTop">
                                        <items>
                                            <Text text="{i18n>newUserLabel}" />
                                            <Link text="{i18n>newUserLink}" class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin" press="onNewUserLinkPress"/>
                                        </items>
                                    </HBox>
                                    <HBox alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center" class="sapUiSmallMarginTop">
                                        <items>
                                            <Text text="{i18n>forgotPasswordLabel}" />
                                            <Link text="{i18n>forgotPasswordLink}" class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin" press="onForgotPassLinkPress" />
                                        </items>
                                    </HBox>
                                </items>
                            </VBox>
                        </items>
                    </FlexBox>
                </content>
            </Page>
            <Page title="{i18n>cockpitPageTitle}" id="pageCockpit" class="sapUiContentPadding">
                <headerContent>
                    <Button text="{i18n>logoffBtn}" icon="sap-icon://log" press="onLogoffBtnPress" />
                </headerContent>
                <content>
                    <HBox>
                        <items>
                            <GenericTile header="{i18n>tileItemsMgmt}" press="onTileItemMgmtPress" class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd">
                                <tileContent>
                                    <TileContent>
                                        <content>
                                            <ImageContent src="sap-icon://product" />
                                        </content>
                                    </TileContent>
                                </tileContent>
                            </GenericTile>
                            <GenericTile header="{i18n>tileProfessionalMgmt}" press="onTileProfMgmtPress" class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd">
                                <tileContent>
                                    <TileContent>
                                        <content>
                                            <ImageContent src="sap-icon://employee" />
                                        </content>
                                    </TileContent>
                                </tileContent>
                            </GenericTile>
                            <GenericTile header="{i18n>tileUserProfile}" subheader="{i18n>tileUserProfSubheader}" press="onTilePartProfPress" class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd">
                                <tileContent>
                                    <TileContent>
                                        <content>
                                            <ImageContent src="sap-icon://business-card" />
                                        </content>
                                    </TileContent>
                                </tileContent>
                            </GenericTile>
                            <GenericTile header="{i18n>tileReviewMode}" press="onTileReviewModePress" class="sapUiSmallMarginEnd">
                                <tileContent>
                                    <TileContent>
                                        <content>
                                            <ImageContent src="sap-icon://favorite" />
                                        </content>
                                    </TileContent>
                                </tileContent>
                            </GenericTile>
                        </items>
                    </HBox>
                </content>
            </Page>
            <Page title="{i18n>itemMgmtPageTitle}" id="pageItemsMgmt" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress" noDataText="{i18n>tableItemsNoData}">
                <headerContent>
                    <Button icon="sap-icon://add" press="onAddItemPress" />
                    <Button icon="sap-icon://refresh" press="onRefreshItemsPress" />
                </headerContent>
                <content>
                    <Table>
                        <columns>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnItem}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnDesc}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnResp}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnAux}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnCurReview}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                        </columns>
                    </Table>
                </content>
            </Page>
            <Page title="{i18n>profMgmtPageTitle}" id="pageProfMgmt" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress" noDataText="{i18n>tableProfNoData}">
                <headerContent>
                    <Button icon="sap-icon://add" press="onAddProfPress" />
                    <Button icon="sap-icon://refresh" press="onRefreshProfPress" />
                </headerContent>
                <content>
                    <Table>
                        <columns>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnName}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnSurname}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnRole}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                            <Column>
                                <header>
                                    <Text text="{i18n>tableColumnCurReview}" />
                                </header>
                            </Column>
                        </columns>
                    </Table>
                </content>
            </Page>
            <Page title="{i18n>newItemPageTitle}" id="pageNewItem" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress">
                <content>
                    <VBox class="sapUiSmallMargin">
                        <f:SimpleForm editable="true" layout="ResponsiveGridLayout" title="{i18n>newItemFormHeader}" labelSpanXL="3" labelSpanL="3" labelSpanM="3" labelSpanS="12" adjustLabelSpan="false" emptySpanXL="4" emptySpanL="4" emptySpanM="4" emptySpanS="0" columnsXL="1" columnsL="1" columnsM="1" singleContainerFullSize="false">
                            <f:content>
                                <Label text="{i18n>newItemDescription}" />
                                <Input />
                                <Label text="{i18n>newItemResponsable}" />
                                <Input />
                                <Label text="{i18n>newItemAuxiliary}" />
                                <Input />
                            </f:content>
                        </f:SimpleForm>
                    </VBox>
                </content>
                <footer>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <content>
                            <ToolbarSpacer />
                            <Button type="Emphasized" text="{i18n>btnSave}" />
                            <Button text="{i18n>btnCancel}" />
                        </content>
                    </Toolbar>
                </footer>
            </Page>
            <Page title="{i18n>newProfPageTitle}" id="pageNewProfessional" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress">
                <content>
                    <VBox class="sapUiSmallMargin">
                        <f:SimpleForm editable="true" layout="ResponsiveGridLayout" title="{i18n>newProfFormHeader}" labelSpanXL="3" labelSpanL="3" labelSpanM="3" labelSpanS="12" adjustLabelSpan="false" emptySpanXL="4" emptySpanL="4" emptySpanM="4" emptySpanS="0" columnsXL="1" columnsL="1" columnsM="1" singleContainerFullSize="false">
                            <f:content>
                                <Label text="{i18n>newProfName}" />
                                <Input />
                                <Label text="{i18n>newProfSurname}" />
                                <Input />
                                <Label text="{i18n>newProfRole}" />
                                <Input />
                            </f:content>
                        </f:SimpleForm>
                    </VBox>
                </content>
                <footer>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <content>
                            <ToolbarSpacer />
                            <Button type="Emphasized" text="{i18n>btnSave}" />
                            <Button text="{i18n>btnCancel}" />
                        </content>
                    </Toolbar>
                </footer>
            </Page>
            <Page id="pageReview" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress">
                <content>
                    <VBox>
                        <items>
                            <Panel headerText="{i18n>highlights}">
                                <content>
                                    <FlexBox id="partnerTopItems" alignItems="Start" justifyContent="Start" />
                                </content>
                            </Panel>
                            <List id="reviewItemsList" noDataText="{i18n>reviewListNoData}">
                                <headerToolbar>
                                    <Toolbar>
                                        <content>
                                            <Title text="{i18n>reviewListHeader}" />
                                        </content>
                                    </Toolbar>
                                </headerToolbar>
                            </List>
                        </items>
                    </VBox>
                </content>
                <footer>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <content>
                            <ToolbarSpacer />
                            <Button text="{i18n>startReviewBtn}" type="Emphasized" press="onStartReviewPress" />
                        </content>
                    </Toolbar>
                </footer>
            </Page>
            <Page id="pagePartnerProfile" title="{i18n>partnerProfileTitle}" showNavButton="true" navButtonPress="onNavButtonPress">
                <content>
                    <VBox class="sapUiSmallMargin">
                        <items>
                            <f:SimpleForm id="SimpleFormChange354wideDual"
                                editable="true"
                                layout="ResponsiveGridLayout"
                                title="{i18n>partnerFormHeader}"
                                labelSpanXL="4"
                                labelSpanL="3"
                                labelSpanM="4"
                                labelSpanS="12"
                                adjustLabelSpan="false"
                                emptySpanXL="0"
                                emptySpanL="4"
                                emptySpanM="0"
                                emptySpanS="0"
                                columnsXL="2"
                                columnsL="1"
                                columnsM="1"
                                singleContainerFullSize="false" >
                                <f:content>
                                    <core:Title text="{i18n>partnerGenDataHeader}" />
                                    <Label text="{i18n>partnerFullName}" />
                                    <Input id="name" value="{SupplierName}" />
                                    <Label text="{i18n>partnerWebsite}" />
                                    <Input value="{Twitter}" />
                                    <core:Title text="{i18n>partnerAddressHeader}" />
                                    <Label text="{i18n>partnerStrtAndNumber}" />
                                    <Input value="{Street}">
                                    </Input>
                                    <Input value="{HouseNumber}">
                                        <layoutData>
                                            <l:GridData span="XL2 L1 M3 S4" />
                                        </layoutData>
                                    </Input>
                                    <Label text="{i18n>partnerZipCity}" />
                                    <Input value="{ZIPCode}">
                                        <layoutData>
                                            <l:GridData span="XL2 L1 M3 S4" />
                                        </layoutData>
                                    </Input>
                                    <Input value="{City}" />
                                    <Label text="{i18n>partnerCountry}" />
                                    <Select id="country" selectedKey="{Country}">
                                        <items>
                                            <core:Item text="Brasil" key="Brasil"/>
                                        </items>
                                    </Select>
                                </f:content>
                            </f:SimpleForm>
                        </items>
                    </VBox>
                </content>
                <footer>
                    <Toolbar>
                        <content>
                            <ToolbarSpacer />
                            <Button text="{i18n>btnSave}" type="Emphasized" />
                            <Button text="{i18n>btnCancel}" />
                        </content>
                    </Toolbar>
                </footer>
            </Page> 
        </pages>
    </App>
</mvc:View>